{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870410/extras/STORY.png?t=1736178889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have been kidnapped and locked in a dark workshop where machines come to life and time flows non-linearly. In <strong>Henry's Forgotten Performance</strong>, you will unravel the terrible secrets of the long abandoned <strong>Freude Corporation</strong>. Use the power of time and decide the fate of the creator of this nightmare. But be careful, everything here has a price.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870410/extras/GAMEPLAY.png?t=1736178889\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Clock Key</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Clock Key</strong> is a unique artifact that allows you to control time within the confines of a mysterious workshop. With it you can:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Slow down enemies</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rewind time</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Duplicating objects</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have to solve <strong>interesting puzzles</strong> related to <strong><i>time</i></strong>, such as how to find an object that disappeared 10 years ago, or how to get into a room that only existed in the past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870410/extras/MYSTERIOS_WORKSHOP_STEAM.png?t=1736178889\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A dark workshop comes to life...</strong> Machines whisper about their creator, and living dolls are hunting you. How far are you willing to go to discover their secret?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.ste